\pard\pardeftab720\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \strokec5 One day Jesus was 
\f0\b praying
\f1\b0  in a certain place. When he finished, one of his disciples said to him, \'93Lord, 
\f0\b teach us to pray
\f1\b0 , just as John taught his disciples.\'94 \'a0Luke 11:1\cf2 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Did you notice that? \'a0These guys spent their lives in a culture that prayed constantly. \'a0\uc0\u8232 \
\ls4\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 They had been exposed to prayer their whole life but at some point they looked at Jesus and said this guy prays differently\'85\uc0\u8232 \
\ls4\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Jesus would you teach us how to pray. \'a0Would you help us take our prayer life to another level. \'a0\uc0\u8232 \
\ls4\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 And Jesus doesn\'92t correct them and tell them that there is no right or wrong way to pray. \'a0He doesn\'92t tell them that really it\'92s just their heart that matters and what they say is irrelevant\'85\uc0\u8232 \
\ls4\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 No\'85He models for them the prayer and a way to pray that many of us know it as the Lord\'92s Prayer. \'a0\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
